#Text=Great update on the traditional Adidas slide shoe .  IMPLICIT Love the addition of the Velcro strap, it provides more support for walking .  IMPLICIT Fantastic purchase !  IMPLICIT
#Text=I ordered some Airforce 1 .  IMPLICIT They came super fast !  IMPLICIT I was emailed through the whole process with updates .  IMPLICIT The shoes are so fire also !  IMPLICIT
#Text=This is a good and easy to slip on sandal .  IMPLICIT I would suggest wearing with socks because the edges of the fabric can dig in a little bit to the skin .  IMPLICIT
#Text=I liked it for the first month .  IMPLICIT after a while my feet would hurt !  IMPLICIT the comfort is okay .  IMPLICIT its soft and doesn't irritate my skin .  IMPLICIT

#Text=Although the shoe is comfortable .  IMPLICIT I can't even walk around the house and the tongue drops off to the side .  IMPLICIT There is nothing to hold it in place and these are supposed to be hiking shoe .  IMPLICIT

#Text=Absolutely loved the design and colors !  IMPLICIT I wish these came in half sizes though . #Text=Fits okay .  IMPLICIT material is good .  IMPLICIT The fresh is not that comfortable that I hoped it to be .  IMPLICIT But, nothing to complain otherwise .  IMPLICIT

#Text=I have always been a Nike fanatic and started getting into Vapormax . IMPLICIT My favorite sneaker by far .  IMPLICIT LOVE LOVE LOVE and fit true to size like a glove :) .  IMPLICIT

#Text=The colors appear dark gray on the shoes and the image when I receive them they were black .  IMPLICIT They were probably one of the most uncomfortable parachutes I've ever tried on .  IMPLICIT They were returned within 72 hours of receiving them IMPLICIT
#Text=Too small especially width  .  IMPLICIT Every one doesn't have narrow feet !  IMPLICIT

#Text=This is the second time I ordered a wide size shoe and was sent a regular size . #Text=The shoe is cute but there is NO stretch to the opening to put your foot in .  IMPLICIT Made it difficult to put on .  IMPLICIT I returned the shoes .  IMPLICIT

#Text=I've worn the gts adrenaline shoes for a couple years now The 2021 design is terrible .  IMPLICIT They are not comfortable .  IMPLICIT My arches of my feet are so sore .  IMPLICIT I never had this issue with past designs .  IMPLICIT I will not buy them again .  IMPLICIT "I'm a nurse and I'm on my feet a lot" IMPLICIT

#Text=I was a little torn on what size to get because so many people said to size up, but I decided to go with my normal size anyway, and I'm glad I did .  IMPLICIT If I had sized up, these would have been too big .  IMPLICIT They did feel a little narrow, especially for a work boot, but I think they'll break in nicely .  IMPLICIT They also look pretty cute if I wanted to go for a lumberchick look, lol .  IMPLICIT
#Text=But didn't work out for me .  IMPLICIT Found another shoe that works better for me .  IMPLICIT
